# INShareFocusStatusIntentResponseCode.inProgress

**Case**

Your intent handler is handling the intent, but it may take some time.

## Declaration

```swift
case inProgress
```

## Handling the Intent

- **INShareFocusStatusIntentResponseCode.success**: Your intent handler successfully updated the user’s communication status.
